Name: Honkstory 2: There was No 1
About the game: Play as Slippery McGee, a clown without limits that can only fight with his fists! Do you have what it takes to slip passed enemies, jump through obstacles, fight malevolent bosses getting in your way of spreading THE FUNNY throughout the universe?! Features • Clowns • Bananas • Retro Beat-Em Up Platformer • 20 Levels, each with their own retrostyle music. • 5 Challenging Bosses
